<b>Create New Key</b><br>
<br>
<label for="purpose">Purpose:</label> <input id="purpose" name="purpose" value="${purpose}"><br>
<label for="user">User (email):</label> <input id="user" name="user" value="${user}"><br>
<label for="passphrase">Passphrase:</label> <input id="passphrase" name="passphrase" value="${passphrase}"><br>
<br>
<button type="button" id="createKey" class="btn btn-success">Create</button> 
<button type="button" id="cancelKeyCreation" class="btn btn-primary">Cancel</button> <br>
<br>
<small>
  User: if you will not share your documents, there is no need to change the username<br>
  Purpose: keys are identified by their purpose<br>
  Passphrase: using the default passphrase is less secure, but convenient<br>
</small>
